ill send this html file to victim and when victim will click on it this account will get Deactivate\n\nVideo POC link:- https://drive.google.com/file/d/12IJOyqVxIOqG_vTWKVJ3qwG7GTn-fV-f/view?usp=sharing\n\n## Impact\n\nAttacker can Deactivate victim premium accounts, And you will lost your good customer for this security flaws","bounty_amount":"300.0","formatted_bounty":"$300","original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":1224851,"file_name":"POC.PNG","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/00heksav11sxo998y4o3l2a8r46v?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22POC.PNG%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27POC.PNG\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQWTIKESA4%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T080857Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECcaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIBdFw7u95MmU3R%2FZBtltwuvKy7D3FduQTxg%2BYOi%2BDG3hAiEApXgrXJvWyPsMBMvP80EMipHB2sHe2NJw%2Bc8H7t%2FeQdkqugUI8P%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDJs6MBIOtcBV33wcRyqOBTIPEjIOv0eedZlcRFFkAcYDkFUG1GB9p%2FMsDSRsgu2XybWA2UCLQzjnzkHf3A8bRxWN8aANYt1dMh49h3EfPXijfpOMneDc3GGDH1OaV6QgHBxRHia8XqCRg5wfoDoqgSI1lT8CHrUcHGyCkBAkmlI80iCWDCM8A28LkBCCe3QR46KKOaNZquMkiODXX0G6dzAqLKOZzNxeYK99x3knTFofSeN3DIA8osuaCQ1U0uyYT5zt%2BLwNXVcZQyfjThvISpFSeOf%2BWYpYy%2Fvgr41TUPYDkdZqoz9kEVjU1wmWDnvIGKgVb1sPWONZvLfQ%2Fhik2qM6e44l6TQwE9rIKFNZLSPd4b1bMLcMrI6xoWXSN6TOX3hLzj49iXPC5tRIXaJhn0B0E3o6O8gAhzv1Pwmgy7C3yCtXmAAvjv6ri8JuUKmBS8vfI01iIjRPNeqOigHJ8X5w%2FTANjfqs7cy89MlDEH47TuKQOUs4ud5wF6wC%2F76ZDxdNIcGtwMWz4HjX1LkSJm0OrMlbso%2Fl1EInS4xddWeQvs3kP05GrXjnjNgZVAz5L64b7jzxkLI9%2FPXydCnPCzWdD7wdC0WtXCJnbBM2piJFXN3BDqnoncwmhSp7GAbmFmU7jmrBG9nuy0NbCa3M1OGglErb0qftbcrhmyvypR5UFtDzomot97vOiXGsI4QstHjanxi9lJfEZIb2lYDL2tAJTYhe%2FOEkPHs8zWSKPhfHQcpNrRWcpngSDQOumK67wV%2B6HED4A6dsX%2B0chUzUt%2F5l%2Bq2QtLWa%2FKyAGxG